        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Zest <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter!) and set aside for garnish</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
