    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, squeeze in the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lemon[s]</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon</strong> into wedges</p><p>Add a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and the<strong> grated cheese</strong> to the pan and stir to combine – this is your <strong>lemony risotto</strong></p>",
